Hoist quickly stood up, "I guess." He then turned to Firedrill, "Don't
do anything staining until i've had a chance to check you out buddy."
But was dissapointed when Firedrill's ussual cheer wasnt recipricated.
He transformed and quickly rolled out.

Firedrill nodded to the Tripredicus, then solemnly and shakily walked
out of the base, waiting for his ride.
